OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA clear
OL,6,Fevening with high cloud clearing away
OL,7,Fwith patchy low cloud developing in
OL,8,Fthe east overnight. Some mist and fog
OL,9,Fforming in prone clear spots, with a
OL,10,Fgrass frost in places.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FAny mist, fog and low cloud
OL,13,Fwill clear quickly after sunrise.
OL,14,FAnother bright and sunny day expected
OL,15,Fwith temperatures slightly higher than
OL,16,FThursday. Winds easing through the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
